        <description>&lt;img src="https://caxlee.github.io/hugo/images/articles/69f5a6df-c335-4198-b405-3b55fa15c90a.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Study could lead to LLMs that are better at complex reasoning" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://caxlee.github.io/hugo/images/articles/69f5a6df-c335-4198-b405-3b55fa15c90a.jpg&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;Study could lead to LLMs that are better at complex reasoning&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;摘要&lt;/strong&gt;: 研究发现测试时训练可显著提高大型语言模型在复杂推理任务上的性能，尤其适用于需要逻辑和推理的挑战性问题。研究者开发了一种框架，利用新任务示例最大化性能提升，可使模型更灵活适应需要规划或抽象的复杂任务。&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
